HEADWORD: Sagapenum
<hw>Sag`a*pe"num</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sagapenon</ets>, <ets>sacopenium</ets>, Gr. <?/: cf. F.
<ets>sagapin</ets>, gomme <ets>sagapin</ets>, sagap⟦eacute⟧num, Ar.
